.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, country, funk, d&b, reggae
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
5 different games are played: poker, scrabble, canasta, bridge, chess
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, accountant, teacher, project-manager, mechanic
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, amaryllis, marigold, poppy
1. the british is the fan of funk
2. the swedish is the person who growsamaryllis
3. the danish is the person playing bridge
4. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of d&b
5. the fan of country is the person playing scrabble
6. the teacher is the person who growstulip
7. the fan of reggae is the accountant
8. the person playing canasta is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia
11. the person who growspoppys is on the left or right of the accountant
12. the journalist is the person playing poker
13. the german is the project-manager
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the fan of electronic
15. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person playing chess

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Music-Genre		|    reggae	|     electronic	|      funk	|     country	|     d&b	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Flower		|     begonia	|    poppy	|     tulip	|     marigold	|      amaryllis	|
| Game	|    chess	|     bridge	|     canasta	|    scrabble	|      poker	|
| Job		|   accountant	|    mechanic	|  teacher	|    project-manager	|   journalist	|
